            "answer_text": "SM- The oldest or second oldest is often chosen as the leader Ex) Irene (Red Velvet) is the oldest, Suho (Exo) is the second oldest, Leeteuk (SUJU) is the oldest, Taeyeon (SNSD) is the oldest JYP- The one who trained longest is the leader Ex) JB (GOT7) trained for 4 years, Jihyo (Twice ) trained for 10 years YG- The one that he thinks will be the most suitable and capable of being the leader, despite of their ages Ex) CL (2NE1) is the third youngest, Yoon (Winner) is the maknae, and GD (Big Bang) is the third oldest. In smaller groups, it\u2019s pretty often that the oldest is the leader, although some may be different Smaller company groups with the oldest as the leader: S.coups (Seventeen) Sowon (Gfriend) Solar (Mamamoo) Shownu (MONSTA X) Smaller company groups that aren\u2019t lead by the oldest: JinJin (ASTRO) Seung Yeon (CLC) ",
